Proto arrived at the battle, seeing the bot immediatly he grinned. "Ah so much carnage to make so little time." He had picked up their chatter on his comm on his way there, "Megatron's brother! You dare give urself any relation to Galvatron you pathetic bot." Proto transformed into Megatron odl version gun and sent a huge blast at Unicrons minions. He then transformed into Rodimus, "The predacons are here to honor our truce Rodimus Prime! Let us end this now when we have the chance!"
